              <p>We power our readers with informations from our large collections of very inspiring, romantic, exciting and captivating books. With us, your brain power is more than doubled as you are informed the right way.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='col-md-3 col-sm-6 highlight'>
            <div class='h-caption'>
              <h4><i class='fa fa-flash fa-5'></i>Quick Read
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div class='h-body text-center'>
              <p>We know the hassles a lot of online readers face when trying to read up their favorite books online, the tiring processes and internet etc. Andelib is super fast with accessibilty, all you need do is Sign Up/IN and request a book.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='col-md-3 col-sm-6 highlight'>
            <div class='h-caption'>
              <h4><i class='fa fa-heart fa-5'></i>Family Love
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div class='h-body text-center'>
              <p>Andelib is a family of book lovers, we share, network, build stronger ties and even more we SACRIFICE, Andelib is the only online library that care about YOU, its no wonder our family is ever-growing.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='col-md-3 col-sm-6 highlight'>
            <div class='h-caption'>
              <h4><i class='fa fa-smile-o fa-5'></i>Andelib's support
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div class='h-body text-center'>
              <p>We are always working round the clock to ensure that our readers are well satisfied, so feel free to contact us for thoe books we don't already have, and be surprised at how quick they are made available to you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- /row -->
      </div>
    </div>
