      <h2 class='text-center top-space'>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <br>
      <div class='row'>
        <div class='col-sm-6'>
          <h3>How much is an Andelib subscription?</h3>
          <p>
            At Andelib, we believe knowledge should be share all around the world and that's why we are absolutely FREE!!!
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='col-sm-6'>
          <h3>Can I make a request for a book?</h3>
          <p>
            Most definitely, Andelib is all about YOU, so contact us today with your book request and we'd have you hooked.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- /row -->
      <div class='row'>
        <div class='col-sm-6'>
          <h3>What is the limit of books to read?</h3>
