            NO, you are not. Andelib offers you umlimited access to our books, so request now and start reading.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='col-sm-6'>
          <h3>Can I make purchase on Andelib?</h3>
          <p>Unfortunately NO, but then why make purchase when you can rent the book .</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- /row -->
      <div class='jumbotron top-space'>
        <h4>“Whatever the cost of our libraries, the price is cheap compared to that of an ignorant nation.” - Walter Cronkite</h4>
        <p class='text-right'>
